5BE%258B%2F&d=DgFN9ivcdgICzBQxXV443i3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=f9909c51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.singtaousa.com/la/13-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/198014-%E3%80%8C%E9%81%93%E6%AD%89%E6%B3%95%E3%80%8D%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E+%E6%88%90%E4%BA%9E%E6%B4%B2%E9%A6%96%E4%BE%8B/</a><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">條例有助官員釋除道歉對法律責任的顧慮</span></span></strong>，希望適時道歉，消除受影響人士的不滿情緖。<br />\n<br />\n  立法會議員涂謹申就指，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不排除有人以道歉去平息事件，用作逃避法律追究，甚至誇大道歉內容以博取信任，難以判斷是否真誠道歉</span></span></strong>，或會影響當事人是否追究的決定。他認為要小心平衡酌情權，以免<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">道歉成為卸責手段</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">面對事實與付出代價，才是真道歉</span></strong><br />\n港共林鄭道歉只係鳩up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭用盡晒道歉法比佢既保護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n林鄭幾識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77de34571b709929114420f501e81e897492f43d","tid":1256712,"uid":90863,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"辛苦巴絲忍辱負重"},{"pid":"2787a42c3eb7a99c52b86c0d2c318e2cba550980","tid":1256712,"uid":6629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:30:17.000Z","msg":"辛苦各位巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff1bc89f1e3056443c07db918f4cee8491962b7","tid":1256712,"uid":158499,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T07:32:39.000Z","msg":"大家面對得公眾，就要有心理準備梗有啲人係反對你，大方點吧巴絲們<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb2ee5da6f525090e1b1597ac367e00c79e00d0","tid":1256712,"uid":219128,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45b0f10faa1708ba01b31b6ea8e81040df2fbf08","tid":1256712,"uid":158301